Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹形圖設計者嚴重損毀?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被敵對勢力擊落了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是因隕石碎片撞擊導致的事故?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是問題所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的問題是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了顛覆計劃的最後一招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.94,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,642)}<Tree Diagram>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便沒有樹形圖設計者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃也依舊能進行這一事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天調查的計劃接手處中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有這棟高樓設施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  是保留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入館編號無法識別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無關人員禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即離開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  果然不會在這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這就完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可以殺你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是市區啊  你還真敢鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼愛逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼愉快地甩著屁股跑人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是在誘惑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就此放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都毀掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現有的以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…將要接手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那聲好響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  我們回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…她的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜謎解解悶如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:04.48,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,644)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提問  一方通行大爺在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反…射…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過確實  默認設定是反射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過和我的本質略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.68,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,644)}<Vector>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確答案是  改變矢量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運動量  熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電流量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的運動僅僅在碰到我的皮膚後就可以發生改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都毀掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到所有的器材 資金 慾望 野心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都真正地灰飛湮滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我意的那天真會到來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.29,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,644)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  又有多少妹妹會死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用什麼方法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即逼停計劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著  是敗者復活戰的題目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將血液流向逆轉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人體會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  你就是實驗對手對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  請多指教
