Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次和超能力者打…很是期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?  槍?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經檢查完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂表現出自己對初戰的熱情道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  雖然已經被允許可以向你開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就開始第一次實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先下手為強了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂說完便開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彈道被改變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂拉開距離開始分析道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他媽在逗我?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這算怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.41,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,644)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這玩意真是超能力者的克隆體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就無視掉她和Original的性能差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過克隆體通過網絡共享著記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會在兩萬場戰鬥中逐漸學習從而進化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許連你都會陷入苦戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來說  我必須得一直和小卒打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃興了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次就只有她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次實驗還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要處理掉身後的實驗體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過處理兩萬個武裝後的克隆體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個實驗才會完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標還未停止活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即繼續進行實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂服從命令道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處理?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止活動?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像…沉入了黑暗的深水之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂…問…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來第一次實驗就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛開始或許有些無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢會變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請你加油來處理下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用考慮太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對方只是藥物和蛋白質合成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  去買個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御…坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像發生案件了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  兇殺?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  還有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不…這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有屍體才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你真的看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是做夢?  怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  哦  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的攝像頭都已經查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有錄到任何可疑事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…剛才還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我們就報告說是目擊者弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  下次我們就會聯繫你的學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  搞些低級的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事啊  靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御…御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然原計劃是完成工作後就回你那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂率先道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是御坂妹妹  這…沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才一直以為你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂確實死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂報告道
