Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防萬一  將進行密碼確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂言出必行地說道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZXC741ASD852QWE963'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂測試道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因無法對剛才的密碼進行解碼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明你不是本實驗的相關人員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂下結論道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個睡袋裡裝的是什麼
