Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是10031號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你昨天和姐姐一起遇到的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂說明道
